                |     Rajeev serves as a legal partner who handles the aspects of a deal, starting from formulating termsheets, and other documentation keeping the interest and safety of the investor as the first priority. Rajeev is a certified chartered accountatn holds CA charter from ICAI. He also has experience teaching students for CA/CS exams.
