            #3_6.panel-collapse.collapse
              .panel-body
                | A wide range of businesses can seek capital through FundMyVenture, from high-growth, technology-driven ventures, to more traditional businesses like retail stores, restaurants and professional services firms, regardless of the business’s stage of growth, whether it be an idea-stage startup or later-stage growth business.
